                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Contoso offers innovative products under the brand \"Contoso Galaxy Innovations.\" One of their featured products is Smart Eyewear, which includes several advanced features:\n\n- **Augmented Reality Interface**: This interface enhances your visual experience by integrating digital information seamlessly into the physical world.\n- **Voice-controlled AI Agent**: Allows for hands-free operation and interaction.\n- **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: Offers high-quality video capability with immersive sound.\n- **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Ensures the user's eyes are protected from harmful light exposure.\n- **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: Provides convenience and longevity for users on the go.\n\nThe Smart Eyewear also includes a comprehensive user guide that covers everything from product overview and fit adjustments to care, maintenance, and troubleshooting. It comes with a two-year limited warranty on all electronic components, and a 30-day return policy.",
